# macOS / editor
.DS_Store
.vscode/
# reference material — kept locally, never built or deployed (large / copyrighted)
/docs/
# brand strategy / presentation decks — reference, not site source
/*.pdf

# analytics exports — local inputs to scripts/generate-video-skeletons.mjs.
# Contain subscriber counts & estimated revenue, so never committed. The
# generated src/content/videos/*.md are committed, so the site builds without these.
# NOTE: leading slash anchors this to the repo-root data/ ONLY — an unanchored
# `data/` would also swallow src/data/ (site config, programs, week themes)!
/data/

# raw brand/design source kept locally, not deployed. The site uses copies:
# logos in public/brand/, the self-hosted script font in public/fonts/. Noto
# Serif TC + Cabin load from Google Fonts (the full CJK .ttf files are ~76MB).
/*.ttf
/Yin Yoga with Katie Design System/

# misc
desktop.ini
*.zip

# design handoff packages + raw brand images — reference, not site source
/design_handoff_library_homepage/
/brand images/
